PHYS-002: Validate coherence_window_us range [1500, 1700]
PHYS-003: Validate spectral_dimension range [1.32, 1.42]
PHYS-004: Validate photonic_band_gap range [0.18, 0.24]
PHYS-005: Validate lock_acquisition_timeout_us = coherence_window_us / 16

Integration Tests
